    <string name="import_csv_instructions">You can create a schedule in Excel, save it as CSV, and import it. The template format requires:\nOne row per time slot, comma-separated, column order:\nCourse Name, Teacher, Classroom, Day of Week (1-7), Start Period (1-12), End Period (1-12), comma-separated weeks...\nExample: Calculus, Prof. Li, Room 302, 1, 1, 2, 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8</string>
